summary: An ordinance accepting a deed from Allen Peyser and wife, for a portion of Lots 5 and 6, Block 92, Carleton Park Addition, for street purposes; setting aside the abutting alley for street use; renaming West Barton Street, from 32nd Avenue West to 34th Avenue West and laying off and establishing West Lynn Street, between 32nd Avenue West and 33rd Avenue West.
